#### **Create a project to display the daily specials for “your” diner.**

* Add title block to the top of your code

  'Tim Rossiter

  'RCET0265

  'Spring 2020

  'Diner Menu Program

  '[https://github.com/rosstimo/](https://github.com/rosstimo/TJR-VS-S20)DinerMenu.git


* Make up a name for your diner and display it in a label at the top of the form.

* Add a label to display the appropriate special depending on the button that is pressed.

* Use buttons to display • Soup of the Day • Chef's Special • Daily Fish 

* Name program elements exactly as follows:

  * DinerMenu.sln

  * DinerMenuForm.vb

  * SoupButton

  * SaladButton

  * FishButton

  * ExitButton

  * DinerNameLabel

  * DisplaySpecialLabel

   

  Sample Data: Dorothy's Diner is offering Tortilla Soup, a California Cobb Salad, and Hazelnut Coated Mahi Mahi.
